        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Arl8 mutants show a dramatic decrease in transport of synaptic vesicle precursor transport vesicles (SVPs) into axons (retention in proximal axon stretch) as compared to wild type when SVP trafficking was monitored using GFP-Rab3 as a surrogate marker in intact C elegans.. Experimental description: Material and Methods \"Images of fluorescently tagged fusion proteins were captured in live C. elegans\"" ;
